Side Effects: This medication made me a complete utter zombie and made me have memory loss. I would fall asleep anywhere and everywhere on a regular basis and forget where I was. I'm generally an upbeat spirit but caused me to be very dull and numb for days that my family got concerned. I would not recommend it what so ever.
